'''L. Neil Smith''' was a science-fiction writer. In the ''Star Wars'' universe, he has written ''[[Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu]]'', ''[[Lando Calrissian and the Flamewind of Oseon]]'', and ''[[Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka]]''. They would later be reprinted in an omnibus edition, [[The Lando Calrissian Adventures (omnibus)|''The Lando Calrissian Adventures'']].

